<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fish! on VRChat — Your New Favorite Place to Unwind</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Zen+Kaku+Gothic+New:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --twilight-deep: #0d1b2e;
    --twilight-mid: #1a2d47;
    --twilight-blue: #2a4a72;
    --horizon-orange: #e8853a;
    --horizon-gold: #f4b942;
    --water-teal: #4a8fa8;
    --mist-white: #e8eef5;
    --soft-text: #c4d4e8;
    --accent-glow: #ff9e5e;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--twilight-deep);
    color: var(--mist-white);
    font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(13,27,46,0.9), transparent);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--horizon-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .logo span { color: var(--mist-white); font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--horizon-orange);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-glow); transform: scale(1.03); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 600px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Simulated atmospheric video background using layered CSS animation */
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      #0d1b2e 0%,
      #1a2d47 20%,
      #2a4a72 40%,
      #e8853a 60%,
      #f4b942 72%,
      #4a8fa8 78%,
      #2a4a72 90%,
      #1a2d47 100%
    );
    animation: sunsetShift 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes sunsetShift {
    0%   { filter: hue-rotate(0deg) brightness(0.85); }
    50%  { filter: hue-rotate(-8deg) brightness(1.05); }
    100% { filter: hue-rotate(8deg) brightness(0.9); }
  }

  /* Animated water ripple layer */
  .hero-water {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 45%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(74,143,168,0.4) 0%, rgba(26,45,71,0.85) 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-water::before, .hero-water::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -100%; right: -100%;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(244,185,66,0.6), transparent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: ripple 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .hero-water::after { animation-delay: 3s; top: 30%; }
  .hero-water::before { top: 55%; }
  @keyframes ripple {
    0% { transform: scaleX(0.3) translateX(80%); opacity: 0; }
    50% { opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: scaleX(1) translateX(-20%); opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Floating orbs simulating bokeh/fireflies */
  .bokeh { position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  .bokeh-dot {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(244,185,66,0.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: float var(--dur, 8s) ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    opacity: var(--op, 0.4);
  }
  @keyframes float {
    0%   { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateY(calc(var(--dy, -20px))) translateX(calc(var(--dx, 10px))); }
  }

  /* Silhouette dock / scene overlay */
  .hero-scene {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 55%;
    background:
      /* dock silhouette */
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 10% at 50% 95%, rgba(13,27,46,0.6) 0%, transparent 100%),
      /* distant treeline */
      linear-gradient(to top, rgba(13,27,46,0.9) 0%, rgba(13,27,46,0.5) 30%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative; z-index: 10;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 24px;
    max-width: 720px;
    animation: fadeUp 1.2s ease 0.3s both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--horizon-gold);
    background: rgba(244,185,66,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(244,185,66,0.3);
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--mist-white);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 40px rgba(232,133,58,0.35);
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--horizon-gold);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: var(--soft-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .cta-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--horizon-orange), var(--horizon-gold));
    color: var(--twilight-deep);
    font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.35s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(232,133,58,0.4);
  }
  .cta-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(232,133,58,0.55);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    color: var(--soft-text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 16px 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,212,232,0.25);
    border-radius: 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: transparent;
    font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
  }
  .cta-secondary:hover { border-color: rgba(196,212,232,0.6); color: var(--mist-white); }

  .platform-hint {
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(196,212,232,0.45);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* ── SCROLL INDICATOR ── */
  .scroll-ind {
    position: absolute; bottom: 32px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    color: rgba(196,212,232,0.4);
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: bounce 2.5s ease infinite;
  }
  .scroll-ind svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%,100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(6px); }
  }

  /* ── FEATURES ── */
  .features {
    position: relative;
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--twilight-deep) 0%, #0a1520 100%);
  }

  .features-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--water-teal);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .feature-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .feature-block.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .feature-block:nth-child(even) { direction: rtl; }
  .feature-block:nth-child(even) > * { direction: ltr; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .feature-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; direction: ltr !important; }
    .feature-block > * { direction: ltr !important; }
  }

  .feature-visual {
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
  }

  /* Atmospheric illustrated placeholders */
  .fv-1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d2840 0%, #1a4a6e 40%, #4a8fa8 70%, #e8853a 100%); }
  .fv-2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2010 0%, #1a4a2a 40%, #2a7a3e 70%, #4a9a5e 100%); }
  .fv-3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2a2a4e 40%, #3a4a7e 70%, #5a6aae 100%); }

  .feature-visual::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    font-size: 5rem; opacity: 0.7; z-index: 2;
    animation: iconFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  @keyframes iconFloat {
    from { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) translateY(-6px); }
    to   { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) translateY(6px); }
  }

  .feature-glow {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 60px rgba(244,185,66,0.12);
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .feature-text { padding: 8px 0; }

  .feature-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--horizon-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .feature-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--mist-white);
  }

  .feature-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--horizon-gold); }

  .feature-text p {
    color: var(--soft-text);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 440px;
  }

  .feature-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--water-teal);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,143,168,0.35);
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── SOCIAL PROOF ── */
  .social-proof {
    padding: 80px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a1520 0%, #0d1b2e 100%);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,143,168,0.12);
  }

  .quote-block {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: var(--horizon-gold);
    opacity: 0.25;
    line-height: 0.5;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--mist-white);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .quote-attr {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(196,212,232,0.45);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .stat-row {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 60px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding-top: 60px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,143,168,0.1);
  }

  .stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    color: var(--horizon-gold);
    display: block;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(196,212,232,0.5);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* ── FINAL CTA ── */
  .final-cta {
    padding: 120px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d1b2e 0%, #0a1218 50%, #0d1b2e 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .final-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    width: 600px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(232,133,58,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .final-cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .final-cta h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--horizon-gold); }

  .final-cta p {
    color: var(--soft-text);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    padding: 32px 40px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,143,168,0.1);
    background: #08111d;
  }

  footer p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(196,212,232,0.3); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  footer a { color: rgba(196,212,232,0.4); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.75rem; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--soft-text); }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; }

  /* ── AMBIENT AUDIO TOGGLE ── */
  .audio-toggle {
    position: fixed; bottom: 28px; right: 28px; z-index: 50;
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    background: rgba(26,45,71,0.85);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,143,168,0.35);
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    color: var(--soft-text);
  }
  .audio-toggle:hover { background: rgba(42,74,114,0.9); }

  /* ── MODAL ── */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 200;
    background: rgba(13,27,46,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .modal-overlay.active { display: flex; }
  .modal {
    background: var(--twilight-mid);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,143,168,0.3);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 48px 40px;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 90%;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease both;
  }
  .modal h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .modal p { color: var(--soft-text); margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .modal-btns { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .modal-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .modal-btn-meta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--horizon-orange), var(--horizon-gold));
    color: var(--twilight-deep);
  }
  .modal-btn-meta:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(232,133,58,0.4); }
  .modal-btn-steam {
    background: rgba(74,143,168,0.15);
    color: var(--mist-white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,143,168,0.35);
  }
  .modal-btn-steam:hover { background: rgba(74,143,168,0.25); }
  .modal-close {
    margin-top: 20px;
    background: none; border: none;
    color: rgba(196,212,232,0.4);
    font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .modal-close:hover { color: var(--soft-text); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVIGATION -->
<nav>
  <div class="logo">Fish! <span>on VRChat</span></div>
  <button class="nav-cta" onclick="openModal()">Jump In For Free</button>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-water"></div>

  <!-- Bokeh particles -->
  <div class="bokeh" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="bokeh-dot" style="width:8px;height:8px;top:22%;left:15%;--dur:9s;--op:0.5;--dy:-18px;--dx:12px;"></div>
    <div class="bokeh-dot" style="width:5px;height:5px;top:35%;left:75%;--dur:11s;--op:0.35;--dy:-24px;--dx:-8px;"></div>
    <div class="bokeh-dot" style="width:10px;height:10px;top:55%;left:60%;--dur:7s;--op:0.3;--dy:-14px;--dx:20px;"></div>
    <div class="bokeh-dot" style="width:6px;height:6px;top:18%;left:45%;--dur:13s;--op:0.45;--dy:-20px;--dx:-15px;"></div>
    <div class="bokeh-dot" style="width:4px;height:4px;top:42%;left:28%;--dur:8s;--op:0.6;--dy:-10px;--dx:6px;"></div>
    <div class="bokeh-dot" style="width:7px;height:7px;top:68%;left:85%;--dur:10s;--op:0.25;--dy:-16px;--dx:-10px;"></div>
    <div class="bokeh-dot" style="width:12px;height:12px;top:30%;left:88%;--dur:14s;--op:0.2;--dy:-22px;--dx:-5px;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scene"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="hero-kicker">Fish! · VRChat · Free to Play</span>
    <h1>Your new favorite place<br>to <em>unwind.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Kick back, catch some fish, and hang out with friends in<br>VRChat's most relaxing world.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <button class="cta-primary" onclick="openModal()">🎣 Jump In For Free</button>
    </div>
    <p class="platform-hint" id="platform-hint">Available on Meta Quest &amp; PC via Steam</p>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-ind">
    <span>Explore</span>
    <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features">
  <div class="features-inner">
    <p class="section-label">Why players keep coming back</p>

    <!-- Feature 1 -->
    <div class="feature-block">
      <div class="feature-visual fv-1">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌅</div>
        <div class="feature-glow"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <div class="feature-number">01 / 03</div>
        <h2>No pressure,<br>just <em>vibes.</em></h2>
        <p>Drop in whenever, leave whenever. There's no meta to master, no leaderboard breathing down your neck. Cast a line, listen to the water, and just… be. Fish! is the VR world you log into when you need to remember why you play games in the first place.</p>
        <span class="feature-tag">Drop-in · Drop-out</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 2 -->
    <div class="feature-block">
      <div class="feature-visual fv-2">
        <div class="feature-icon">🏔️</div>
        <div class="feature-glow"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <div class="feature-number">02 / 03</div>
        <h2>Find your <em>spot.</em></h2>
        <p>From mist-wrapped mountain lakes to glowing bioluminescent night coves, every biome in Fish! is a world worth losing yourself in. Each location has its own atmosphere, its own sounds, its own secret catches. Explore until you find the one that feels like yours.</p>
        <span class="feature-tag">Multiple Biomes</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 3 -->
    <div class="feature-block">
      <div class="feature-visual fv-3">
        <div class="feature-icon">🫂</div>
        <div class="feature-glow"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <div class="feature-number">03 / 03</div>
        <h2>Better with <em>friends.</em></h2>
        <p>Share a dock with someone across the world. Talk, laugh, sit in comfortable silence. Full spatial voice chat means every shared catch feels real. Fish! has become one of VRChat's most loved social spaces — not despite how quiet it is, but because of it.</p>
        <span class="feature-tag">Spatial Voice Chat</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOCIAL PROOF -->
<section class="social-proof">
  <div class="quote-block">
    <span class="quote-mark">"</span>
    <p class="quote-text">I've logged more hours in Fish! than any game this year. It's the first thing I open when I need to decompress.</p>
    <p class="quote-attr">— Top-rated VRChat user review</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="stat">
